    "english": "Twenty-five years after the assassination of her son Olivier in 1977, Nicole Parmentier decides to meet with Eric Gaubert who has just been released from jail after having served his time for these crime. An explosive encounter behind closed doors between two damaged and fragile protagonists that destiny has forced together."
